node.text: WATCH THIS🎥 Short tutorial on how to fillet aka remove fish cheeks (a delicacy) This method will work on large snapper species and grouper species too! Best knife to use for this is @smithsconsumerproducts 4” bait breaker.🔪🐟 Most likely, you’re throwing out the BEST part of any snapper/grouper you harvest!! Try this with your next catch and cook it up any way you like! Melts in your mouth, so tender🤤🙌🐟 #darcizzle #fishfillet #smithsconsumerproducts #fillet #freshfish #muttonsnapper #howtovideo #ladyangler #videotutorial #darcizzleoffshore

node.title: How to Fillet FISH CHEEKS!! Best Part of the Fish!

node.text: WHICH NET?? I get asked a lot what cast net folks should buy. There are a number of factors that are important to consider before you purchase a cast net. node.text: In this how to video, I go over cast netting.🕸 How to throw a cast net using the triple load method.🎥 And NO- you don’t have to put the cast net in your mouth. Watch & learn! Throwing a cast net is an  ESSENTIAL SKILL every angler should learn. PS- If I wasn’t talking, it would’ve been under a minute🤗 Turn up the volume & I hope you learn a trick or two!!💯👍🐟 #darcizzle #castnet #bait #baitfish #baitcasting #howtovideo #minute #oneminute #ladyangler #angler #darcizzleoffshore
